  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And finally, we have some cousins in the woods, and-- too, in the-- in the village.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And finally, they-- my cousins, they-- they killed the father and the brother.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They killed both of them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then finally, they-- they told us to find the cousins.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We went to look for them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We don't find them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Me and my brother, no.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We find two men that was waiting for us, because when the winter supposed-- they are afraid for the winter.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Some people afraid for the winter.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They went back to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And when they start to kill in Grodno ghetto, they run back to the woods again.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they know-- they've been already in the summertime-- they know in that place they will meet somebody.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Finally, I know the wood people for quite a while.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they start to beg us to show the place.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They don't need our help, just to show they going to be close to us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Finally, when we come in, the-- the-- we took him-- from the beginning, I said, we can-- we've got to ask permission.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It's not allowed to do it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And then they start to beg and everything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We know them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They're Jewish.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We brought them in in our place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And down there was playing a little girl, was [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Tanya. ?] Found her too, in the woods.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "She was belonging to the-- to that leader in the-- from the group.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I have a thing [INAUDIBLE] down there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And she went down there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And she said, Abel and Jacob brought two men.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Abel and Jacob brought two men.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Then the leader comes up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "He was our leader.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "When I was laying down to rest like in a doghouse, like a doghouse.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
